high_descs: Turn to your right, walk past the fridge, then turn left.
Pick up the potato from the counter.
Turn around and walk to the microwave.
Warm the potato in the microwave, then take it out again.
Turn right, walk, then turn around and walk towards the fridge.
Place the potato on the middle shelf of the fridge, next to the lettuce.
anns.task_desc: Place a warmed potato in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the counter on the right of the fridge.
Pick up the potato from the counter.
Turn around and walk to the microwave.
Place to potato in the microwave, turn the microwave on and wait before removing it.
Turn around and walk to the fridge.
Place the potato in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Place a warmed potato in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn to your right and walk over to the kitchen counter to the right of the fridge.
Pick up the potato that is on the kitchen counter.
Turn around and walk over to the kitchen sink.
Place the potato in the microwave above the kitchen sink and heat it before taking it back out.
Turn around and walk over to the fridge.
Place the potato in the fridge to the right of the lettuce.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooked potato into the refrigerator.
